                CSTA
            </a>
            <nav class="main-nav">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/library">Resources</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/request">Submit</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <div class="header-actions">
                <button class="btn btn-outline login-btn">Log In</button>
                <button class="mobile-menu-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="mobile-menu">
        <button class="close-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
        </button>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/library">Resources</a></li>
            <li><a href="/request">Submit</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Discover the Best CS Teaching Tools</h1>
                <p>A curated library of top-quality resources for computer science education, reviewed and rated by teachers like you.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="/library" class="btn">Explore Resources</a>
                    <a href="/request" class="btn btn-outline">Submit a Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
            <div id="canvas-container"></div>
        </div>
    </section>
  

    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>Why Use Our Resources Library?</h2>
                <p>Discover how our platform makes finding the perfect CS teaching resources easier than ever.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card" id="feature-1">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-filter"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Filterable Database</h3>
                    <p>Quickly find exactly what you need with our comprehensive filtering system based on grade level, price, language, and more.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card" id="feature-2">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Crowdsourced Submissions</h3>
                    <p>Our community of educators continuously adds new resources to ensure you have access to the latest tools.</p>
                    <span class="feature-tag badge-new">New</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card" id="feature-3">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Teacher-Driven Reviews</h3>
                    <p>Real reviews from real teachers who have used these resources in their classrooms.</p>
                    <span class="feature-tag badge-new">New</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card" id="feature-4">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Vetting System</h3>
                    <p>Every resource undergoes a thorough review process by our team of experts to ensure quality.</p>
                    <span class="feature-tag badge-new">New</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card" id="feature-5">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-align-left"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Standards Alignment</h3>
                    <p>Find resources that align with CSTA and Common Core standards to meet your curriculum needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card" id="feature-6">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
                    <p>Access our library on any device, whether you're planning at home or searching in the classroom.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="how-it-works">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p>Our platform makes finding and sharing CS resources simple and efficient</p>
            </div>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step" id="step-1">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <h3>Search & Filter</h3>
                    <p>Use our powerful search and filtering tools to find resources that match your specific needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step" id="step-2">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <h3>Review Details</h3>
                    <p>Read comprehensive information, standards alignment, and authentic teacher reviews.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step" id="step-3">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <h3>Try Resources</h3>
                    <p>Follow links to try resources directly or download materials for your classroom.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step" id="step-4">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <h3>Share Feedback</h3>
                    <p>Add your own reviews and ratings to help other educators make informed decisions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>Growing Community</h2>
                <p>Join thousands of educators already using our platform</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card" id="stat-1">
                    <div class="stat-number">600+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Resources</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card" id="stat-2">
                    <div class="stat-number">15,000+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Educators</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card" id="stat-3">
                    <div class="stat-number">8,500+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Reviews</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card" id="stat-4">
                    <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Countries</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Enhance Your CS Teaching?</h2>
            <p>Join our community of educators and gain access to our ever-growing library of quality resources.</p>
            <a href="/library" class="btn">Start Exploring Today</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-about">
                    <a href="#" class="footer-logo">
                        CSTA Resources
                    </a>
                    <p>Our mission is to empower computer science educators with high-quality, vetted resources to enhance teaching and learning experiences.</p>
                    <div class="footer-social">
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links-col">
                    <h4 class="footer-heading">Resources</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="#">Browse All</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Submit Resource</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Standards</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Featured Tools</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links-col">
                    <h4 class="footer-heading">Community</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="#">Educators</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Chapters</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Events</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Forums</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links-col">
                    <h4 class="footer-heading">Company</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Terms of Service</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>© 2025 CSTA Resources Library. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>Made with ❤️ for CS educators worldwide</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Login Modal -->
    <div class="modal" id="login-modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h3 class="modal-title">Log In</h3>
                <button class="modal-close">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <form id="login-form">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="username" class="form-label">username</label>
                    <input type="text" id="username" name="username"class="form-input" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" class="form-input" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-footer">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn">Log In</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    
